 clang/include/clang/Sema/Sema.h               |  2 +
 clang/lib/Sema/SemaChecking.cpp               | 46 +++++++++++
 clang/lib/Sema/SemaExpr.cpp                   |  5 ++
 .../read-image-integer-linear-filter.cl       | 80 +++++++++++++++++++
